{
  "stem": "27409.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were not many, three Jews in the whole-- my year, reading maths and physics.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "One of our professors, Professor Dr.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Nicolescu, he was, afterwards, president of the Romanian Academy of Sciences.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He protested.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we had a good seat in the front.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We were not many students.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You see, the gentiles didn't go for mathematics.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So we were three.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And one left during the year to go to Japan.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we had two left.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were secretly in Jewish student societies, Zionist student societies, but officially not permitted.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My grandfather was a very hot Zionist and always active, like my uncles, parents.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "September.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They wanted me to go to, as I said, go in Palestine.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But-- again, a but-- you needed 40,000 leu, in order to go as a sort of capitalist, which like I couldn't afford.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the Zionist organization collected some money.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was a auction, if you could call it so, to find somebody from the candidates to go.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A young chap, a friend of mine, Yehuda Sherman, Little Sherman, then.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Today, he's Yehuda [NON-ENGLISH], a well-known politician in Israel.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was minister.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He went.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I stood on.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He will come later in my life, again appear.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And would there not have been a possibility of you going to Palestine, then, on one of the Youth Aliyah schemes, without paying so much?",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were not organized, Youth Aliyah.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You see, they were considered mostly German.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they had to take from German-occupied territory, Germany, Austria, to take out the Jewish youngsters.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And from our towns, we went to [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I had a cousin who went.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But they were older.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then, the idea was of, you finish your studies, and it would be better for you.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You come as a--",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
